	  <concept id="id1617MD00S3U"
            ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3"
            class="- topic/topic concept/concept ">
		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">13.003</ph> Policy.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <ol id="d724e13" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d738e17" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Agencies shall use simplified acquisition procedures to the maximum extent practicable for all purchases of supplies or services not exceeding the simplified acquisition threshold (including purchases at or below the micro-purchase threshold). This policy does not apply if an agency can meet its requirement using-</p>
					          <ol id="d724e23" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d738e27" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Required sources of supply under <xref href="FAR-i1118293.dita#i1118293"
                              base="i1118293"
                              outputclass="fm:Part"
                              class="- topic/xref ">partÂ  8</xref> (<i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">e.g.,</i> Federal Prison Industries, Committee for Purchase from People Who are Blind or Severely Disabled, and Federal Supply Schedule contracts);</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d738e42" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Existing indefinite delivery/indefinite quantity contracts; or</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d738e51" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Other established contracts.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li props="Runin" class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d738e62" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            
					          </p>
					          <ol id="d724e68" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d738e72" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Acquisitions of supplies or services that have an anticipated dollar value exceeding $3,500 ($20,000 for acquisitions as described in <xref href="FAR-i1111870.dita#i1111870"
                              base="i1111870"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">13.201</xref>(g)(1)) but not exceeding $150,000 ($750,000 for acquisitions described in paragraph (1)(i) of the simplified acquisition threshold definition at <xref href="FAR-i1125359.dita#i1125359"
                              base="i1125359"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">2.101</xref>) are reserved exclusively for small business concerns and shall be set aside (see <xref href="FAR-i1101771.dita#i1101771"
                              base="i1101771"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">19.000</xref>, <xref href="FAR-i1101696.dita#i1101696"
                              base="i1101696"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">19.203</xref>, and subpart <xref href="FAR-i1100723.dita#i1100723"
                              base="i1100723"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">19.5</xref>).</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d738e97" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                The contracting officer may make an award to a small business concern under the-</p>
							              <ol id="d724e103" class="- topic/ol ">
								                <li class="- topic/li ">
									                  <p id="d738e107" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(i)</ph>
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
										                    8(a) Program (see subpart <xref href="FAR-i1099848.dita#i1099848"
                                    base="i1099848"
                                    outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                                    class="- topic/xref ">19.8</xref>);</p>
								                </li>
								                <li class="- topic/li ">
									                  <p id="d738e119" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(ii)</ph>
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
										                    Historically Underutilized Business Zone (HUBZone) Program (but see <xref href="FAR-i1099604.dita#i1099604"
                                    base="i1099604"
                                    outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                                    class="- topic/xref ">19.1305</xref> and <xref href="FAR-i1099639.dita#i1099639"
                                    base="i1099639"
                                    outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                                    class="- topic/xref ">19.1306</xref>(a)(4));</p>
								                </li>
								                <li class="- topic/li ">
									                  <p id="d738e134" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(iii)</ph>
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
										                    Service-Disabled Veteran-Owned Small Business (SDVOSB) Program (see subpart <xref href="FAR-i1099391.dita#i1099391"
                                    base="i1099391"
                                    outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                                    class="- topic/xref ">19.14</xref>); or</p>
								                </li>
								                <li class="- topic/li ">
									                  <p id="d738e146" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(iv)</ph>
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
										                    Women-Owned Small Business (WOSB) Program (see <xref href="FAR-i1099174.dita#i1099174"
                                    base="i1099174"
                                    outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                                    class="- topic/xref ">subpartÂ  19.15</xref>).</p>
								                </li>
							              </ol>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d738e160" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                The following contracting officerâs decisions for acquisitions at or below the simplified acquisition threshold are not subject to review under subpart <xref href="FAR-i1101036.dita#i1101036"
                              base="i1101036"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">19.4</xref>:</p>
							              <ol id="d724e169" class="- topic/ol ">
								                <li class="- topic/li ">
									                  <p id="d738e173" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(i)</ph>
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
										                    A decision not to make an award under the 8(a) Program.</p>
								                </li>
								                <li class="- topic/li ">
									                  <p id="d738e182" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(ii)</ph>
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
										                    A decision not to set aside an acquisition for HUBZone small business concerns, service-disabled veteran-owned small business concerns, or EDWOSB concerns and WOSB concerns eligible under the WOSB Program.</p>
								                </li>
							              </ol>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d738e193" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(4)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Each written solicitation under a set-aside shall contain the appropriate provisions prescribed by part <xref href="FAR-i1101928.dita#i1101928"
                              base="i1101928"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">19</xref>. If the solicitation is oral, however, information substantially identical to that in the provision shall be given to potential quoters.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li props="Runin" class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d738e207" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            
					          </p>
					          <ol id="d724e213" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d738e217" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                The contracting officer shall not use simplified acquisition procedures to acquire supplies and services if the anticipated award will exceed-</p>
							              <ol class="- topic/ol ">
								                <li class="- topic/li ">
									                  <p id="d738e227" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(i)</ph>
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
										                    The simplified acquisition threshold; or</p>
								                </li>
								                <li class="- topic/li ">
									                  <p id="d738e236" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(ii)</ph>
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
										                    $7 million ($13 million for acquisitions as described in <xref href="FAR-i1111260.dita#i1111260"
                                    base="i1111260"
                                    outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                                    class="- topic/xref ">13.500</xref>(c)), including options, for acquisitions of commercial items using <xref href="FAR-i1111258.dita#i1111258"
                                    base="i1111258"
                                    outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                                    class="- topic/xref ">subpartÂ  13.5</xref>.</p>
								                </li>
							              </ol>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d738e253" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Do not break down requirements aggregating more than the simplified acquisition threshold (or for commercial items, the threshold in <xref href="FAR-i1111258.dita#i1111258"
                              base="i1111258"
                              outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                              class="- topic/xref ">subpartÂ  13.5</xref>) or the micro-purchase threshold into several purchases that are less than the applicable threshold merely to-</p>
							              <ol id="d724e265" class="- topic/ol ">
								                <li class="- topic/li ">
									                  <p id="d738e266" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(i)</ph>
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
										                    Permit use of simplified acquisition procedures; or</p>
								                </li>
								                <li class="- topic/li ">
									                  <p id="d738e275" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(ii)</ph>
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
										                    Avoid any requirement that applies to purchases exceeding the micro-purchase threshold.</p>
								                </li>
							              </ol>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d738e288" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            An agency that has specific statutory authority to acquire personal services (see <xref href="FAR-i1077856.dita#i1077856"
                        base="i1077856"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">37.104</xref>) may use simplified acquisition procedures to acquire those services.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d738e300" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(e)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Agencies shall use the Governmentwide commercial purchase card and electronic purchasing techniques to the maximum extent practicable in conducting simplified acquisitions (but see <xref href="FAR-i1080782.dita#i1080782"
                        base="i1080782"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">32.1108</xref>(b)(2)).</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d738e313" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(f)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Agencies shall maximize the use of electronic commerce when practicable and cost-effective (see <xref href="FAR-i1123002.dita#i1123002"
                        base="i1123002"
                        outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                        class="- topic/xref ">subpartÂ  4.5</xref>). Drawings and lengthy specifications can be provided off-line in hard copy or through other appropriate means.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d738e325" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(g)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Authorized individuals shall make purchases in the simplified manner that is most suitable, efficient, and economical based on the circumstances of each acquisition. For acquisitions not expected to exceed-</p>
					          <ol id="d724e334" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d738e335" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                The simplified acquisition threshold for other than commercial items, use any appropriate combination of the procedures in <xref href="FAR-i1112458.dita#i1112458"
                              base="i1112458"
                              outputclass="fm:Parts"
                              class="- topic/xref ">partsÂ  13</xref>, <xref href="FAR-i1111055.dita#i1111055"
                              base="i1111055"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">14</xref>, <xref href="FAR-i1109360.dita#i1109360"
                              base="i1109360"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">15</xref>, <xref href="FAR-i1079831.dita#i1079831"
                              base="i1079831"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">35</xref>, or <xref href="FAR-i1079251.dita#i1079251"
                              base="i1079251"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">36</xref>, including the use of <xref href="http://uscode.house.gov/browse.xhtml;jsessionid=114A3287C7B3359E597506A31FC855B3"
                              format="html"
                              scope="external"
                              class="- topic/xref ">Standard Form1442</xref>, Solicitation, Offer, and Award (Construction, Alteration, or Repair), for construction contracts (see <xref href="FAR-i1078213.dita#i1078213"
                              base="i1078213"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">36.701</xref>(a)); or</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d738e366" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                $7 million ($13 million for acquisitions as described in <xref href="FAR-i1111260.dita#i1111260"
                              base="i1111260"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">13.500</xref>(c)), for commercial items, use any appropriate combination of the procedures in <xref href="FAR-i1113784.dita#i1113784"
                              base="i1113784"
                              outputclass="fm:Parts"
                              class="- topic/xref ">partsÂ  12</xref>, <xref href="FAR-i1112458.dita#i1112458"
                              base="i1112458"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">13</xref>, <xref href="FAR-i1111055.dita#i1111055"
                              base="i1111055"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">14</xref>, and <xref href="FAR-i1109360.dita#i1109360"
                              base="i1109360"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">15</xref> (see paragraph (d) of this section).</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d738e393" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(h)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            In addition to other considerations, contracting officers shall-</p>
					          <ol id="d724e402" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d738e403" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Promote competition to the maximum extent practicable (see <xref href="FAR-i1112244.dita#i1112244"
                              base="i1112244"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">13.104</xref>);</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d738e415" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Establish deadlines for the submission of responses to solicitations that afford suppliers a reasonable opportunity to respond (see <xref href="FAR-i1120755.dita#i1120755"
                              base="i1120755"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">5.203</xref>);</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d738e427" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Consider all quotations or offers that are timely received. For evaluation of quotations or offers received electronically, see <xref href="FAR-i1112336.dita#i1112336"
                              base="i1112336"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">13.106-2</xref>(b)(3); and</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d738e439" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(4)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Use innovative approaches, to the maximum extent practicable, in awarding contracts using simplified acquisition procedures.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
		    </conbody>
	  </concept>
